xes.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Sat, 05 Aug 2023 12:38:38 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/money/2023/aug/05/help-with-uk-energy-bills-unlikely-this-winter-suggests-grant-shapps" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/business/2023/aug/05/nostalgia-trip-volvo-estate-owners-reminisce-about-swedish-workhorse-before-its-withdrawal-from-uk-market" target="_blank">‘Nostalgia trip’: Volvo estate owners reminisce about Swedish workhorse before its withdrawal from UK market - The Guardian</a></h2><div class="description"> Carmaker will no longer sell its estate or saloon cars in Britain due to sharp decline in demand. 70 years after the launch of the first Volvo estate, the manufacturer has announced that its days are coming to an end. ‘The appetite for our saloon and estate models has fallen to very low levels in the UK,’ it said.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Sat, 05 Aug 2023 07:00:36 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">entertainment</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/business/2023/aug/05/nostalgia-trip-volvo-estate-owners-reminisce-about-swedish-workhorse-before-its-withdrawal-from-uk-market" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2023/aug/05/former-pakistan-prime-minister-imran-khan-jailed-for-three-years" target="_blank">Imran Khan: former Pakistan prime minister sentenced to three years in jail - The Guardian</a></h2><div class="description"> Imran Khan arrested in Lahore after court ruling bans him from politics for five years for corruption. Imran Khan accused of illegally selling gifts from 